Package org.emoncms

Interface Input

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    HttpInput, MqttInput, RedisInput, SqlInput
    public interface Input
    The Input interface is used to communicate with an emoncms webserver and handle input specific actions. An input instance can be used to
    • Post data to the instanced input.
    • Configure logging or other data processing.
    • Get configuration information.
